Package gloskampen.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MoGlossary
    This class is responsible to handle the quiz data
    MoResult
    This class is responsible for handling the result for a certain quiz
    MoResultList
    This class is responsible for handling all the results for all tests
    MoUser
    This class is responsible for a user
    MoUserList
    This class is responsible to handle a list with users and adding/removing users from the list
    MoWord
    This class is responsible for a certain word between two certain languages
    MoWordList
    This class is responsible for handling a list of all lists of words that the programme has, i.e one entry for a list between Swedish-English, one for Swedish-German etc
